converted_content:
Here's the converted product data in the target API specification format:

```json
{
  "id": "eiffel-tower-stairs-ticket",
  "name": {
    "en": "Eiffel Tower stairs ticket to the second floor"
  },
  "description": {
    "en": "<p>With your ticket to the second floor via the stairs in hand, you are completely free to explore the heart of the Tower's structure. All the charm of Gustave Eiffel's creation and the beauty of the whole of Paris will gradually be revealed as you climb the 674 steps.</p>"
  },
  "highlights": [
    {
      "en": "The cheapest ticket"
    },
    {
      "en": "Discover the Tower in a different way via the stairs"
    }
  ],
  "rating": 0,
  "variants": [
    {
      "id": "stairs-2nd-floor-option",
      "name": {
        "en": "Ticket to the Second Floor via the Stairs"
      },
      "bookingUrl": "https://www.toureiffel.paris/en/rates-opening-times",
      "cancellationPolicy": [],
      "prices": [
        {
          "id": "adult-price",
          "name": {
            "en": "Adult"
          },
          "price": {
            "currency": "EUR",
            "value": 14.2
          }
        },
        {
          "id": "youth-price",
          "name": {
            "en": "Youth (12-24 years)"
          },
          "price": {
            "currency": "EUR",
            "value": 7.1
          }
        },
        {
          "id": "child-price",
          "name": {
            "en": "Child (4-11 years)"
          },
          "price": {
            "currency": "EUR",
            "value": 3.6
          }
        },
        {
          "id": "disabled-price",
          "name": {
            "en": "Disabled visitor"
          },
          "price": {
            "currency": "EUR",
            "value": 3.6
          }
        },
        {
          "id": "free-child",
          "name": {
            "en": "Child (under 4 years)"
          },
          "isFree": true
        }
      ],
      "fulfillmentType": "PICKUP"
    }
  ],
  "media": [
    {
      "url": "https://www.toureiffel.paris/themes/custom/tour_eiffel/img/fb.jpg",
      "type": "IMAGE"
    }
  ],
  "inventoryType": "OFFICIAL"
}
```

Note:
- The `name`, `description`, `highlights`, and `prices.name` fields are converted to use language code keys (e.g., `"en"`) as per the target specification.
- The `rating` field is set to `0` since no rating was provided in the original data.
- The `options` array in the original data is converted to a `variants` array with each option becoming a variant object.
- The `price_options` array is converted to a `prices` array within each variant.
- The `fulfillment_type.pickup` field is converted to a string value `"PICKUP"` in the `fulfillmentType` field of each variant.
- The `related_media` array is converted to a `media` array with the `type` field value changed to `"IMAGE"`.
- The `inventory_types` array is converted to a single string value `"OFFICIAL"` in the `inventoryType` field.
